---
title: Passkey Wallet Session Lifecycle
---
flowchart TD
    A[User visits dapp] --> B{credentialId in IndexedDB?}

    B -- No --> C[Show Connect button]
    C --> D[User clicks → Popup → Create passkey]
    D --> E[PRF → HKDF → protocol keys]
    E --> F[Store credentialId]
    F --> G[PXE syncs from network]

    B -- Yes --> H[Biometric prompt]
    H --> I[PRF → HKDF → same keys]
    I --> J[PXE loads from cache]

    G --> K[Session Active]
    J --> K

    K --> L{User action}
    L -- sendTx --> M[Popup: tx details + Face ID]
    M -- Approve --> N[WebAuthn signs → prove → submit]
    M -- Cancel --> K
    N --> K
    L -- Read balance --> O[Viewing keys decrypt locally]
    O --> K

    K --> P{Page event}
    P -- Refresh --> Q[Memory wiped → biometric again]
    Q --> H
    P -- Tab close --> R[Memory wiped, IndexedDB persists]
